\begin{abstract}

\noindent An understanding of the principles behind the dual dipole antenna is developed using physics and numerical modeling as guidelines. We look at antenna designs and their efficacy using several measures. The efficacy of the dual dipole antenna as compared to the standard dipole antenna is demonstrated. A real-world example is used to illustrate a practical application of this research.

\end{abstract}

